I know this may sound ignorant of me, but this is new to me. Any answers/suggestions/insights will be greatly appreciated. I always look out for what group im in, and do my best to make sure everyone survives. Does that matter at all that much, or is it the guild/people/players you associate with?<br>
None of this is meant to be sarcasm nor is it meant to imply anything...I am merely questioning the &quot;higher end&quot; of the game is all.<br>
<br>
Zeratus Shadowblade<br>
