<br>
Before level 50 it's casual groups and lots of exploring in dungeons and other zones. Basically a vacation in Norrath.<br>
<br>
After level 50 any real challenge involves getting multiple groups of players for some plane or dragon raid. Your group vs the game.<br>
<br>
At level 60 you get to die from mobs with 400,000 HP which hit for 1,100 dmg and are magic immune. Your small army vs Verant the Company.<br>
<br>
*Edit* - Forgot to add. At level 60 you get to sit around the newbie lift in Kelethin for 5 hours trying to forage some rare fruit for your epic weapon. You can also swim around the bottom of Iceclad Ocean looking for a Wooden Plank so you can quest for some big gun you can easily get playing Quake. Has anyone ever found this wood plank??<br>
