<br>
Don't let the message boards fool you.  I've seen people have disagreements here and end up grouping togther when they get online.<br>
<br>
The politics are mainly around a very small percentage of the game content (&lt;5%).  I don't blame the players for this.  It's a design flaw.  When you have 3+ day spawns, sooner or later you are going to have competition to kill them.<br>
<br>
If you want to go to a Plane and your guild isn't going anytime soon, ask a friend to see if you can join him or her on their next raid.  Also, try to get on an open raid.  I've taken an SK friend of mine, who was unguilded, to Fear and he got Planar arms on that trip. <p>Zaboo Krusher<BR>
